title: Are You Willing to do the Andy King

description:
1-8 - Today on the show we had actor Aldis Hodge stop by where he spoke about his movie with Taraji P. Henson "What Men Want", sex scenes, black empowerment and more. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Michelle Rodriguez for defending Liam Neson. Also, since it is Freaky Friday and Andy King from Fyre Fest has been spoke about constantly this week, we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our male listeners would be willing to do an Andy King, in other words are you willing to give fellatio for the team?
